quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Abundance distracts you
  102,2,Until you visit the graveyards
  102,3,"Indeed, you will know"
  102,4,"Certainly, you will know"
  102,5,If you knew with knowledge of certainty
  102,6,You would see the Inferno
  102,7,Then you will see it with the eye of certainty
  102,8,"Then, on that Day, you will be questioned about the Bliss"